h
A'(x) = \lim_{h\to0} \frac{A(x+h) - A(x)}{h} =  \lim_{h\to0}\frac{\int_c^{x+h}f(t)dt - \int_c^{x}f(t)dt}{h} = \lim_{h\to0}\frac{\int_x^{x+h}f(t)dt}{h}
